data.description: Hard to find a home with livability and so many possibilities for income producing. Home was completely remodeled in 2005. Four bedrooms on the main level with an ADA bathroom, laundry room, this level was once used as an adult care home. The upstairs is a private 2 bedroom, siting area bath and laundry. Check with the city to see if you can run your business. It is a great home for a large family. Guest home could be an ADU. The backyard is private with a chicken coop, fruit trees, outbuildings
